    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the <strong>tomato paste </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 20-25 min or until the potato is tender and the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>caldeirada-style stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1641303447492-x200.jpg",
