    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, separate your <strong>parsley & chives</strong>, then chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Zest half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter), then cut the <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Slice your <strong>bread roll[s]</strong> in half and score the cut sides in a criss-cross pattern, taking care not to cut all the way through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1641303451426-x200.jpg",
