    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>peri-peri crusty bread </strong>into triangles</p><p>Serve the <strong>caldeirada-style haddock stew </strong>with the <strong>peri-peri crusty bread </strong>to the side, ready for dipping</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
